h\" style=\"color:#ffe074;font-size:12px;line-height:1.3\"><em>Anche un bambino sa quanto sia preziosa la foresta. L&#8217;odore fresco e mozzafiato degli alberi. Uccelli echeggianti che volano sopra quella densa magnitudine. Un clima stabile, una vita diversificata sostenibile e una fonte di cultura. Tuttavia, le foreste e altri ecosistemi sono in bilico, minacciati di diventare terreni coltivati, pascoli e piantagioni.</em></p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"></div>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n\";s:9:\"protected\";b:0;}s:4:\"meta\";O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:14:\"_crdt_document\";s:0:\"\";s:31:\"jetpack_post_was_ever_published\";b:0;s:13:\"wpop_keywords\";s:0:\"\";s:16:\"wpop_description\";s:44:\"Immagine di sfondo con citazione sovrapposta\";s:19:\"wpop_viewport_width\";i:1200;s:16:\"wpop_block_types\";a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}s:11:\"wpop_locale\";s:5:\"it_IT\";s:15:\"wpop_wp_version\";s:0:\"\";s:25:\"wpop_contains_block_types\";s:75:\"core/column,core/columns,core/cover,core/heading,core/paragraph,core/spacer\";s:9:\"footnotes\";s:0:\"\";}s:14:\"category_slugs\";a:1:{i:0;s:6:\"banner\";}s:13:\"keyword_slugs\";a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"core\";i:1;s:8:\"featured\";}s:15:\"pattern_content\";s:1736:\"<!-- wp:cover {\"url\":\"https://s.w.org/images/core/5.8/forest.jpg\",\"dimRatio\":60,\"minHeight\":800,\"align\":\"full\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull\" style=\"min-height:800px\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-60 has-background-dim\"></span><img class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/5.8/forest.jpg\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" /><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"align\":\"wide\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#ffe074\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"64px\"}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-color\" style=\"color:#ffe074;font-size:64px\">Foresta.</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading --